Lolcats version 0.01
====================

Lolcats converts standard English (English, not American at this moment in time) to Lolcat Pidgin English.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no other modules or libraries.

